headline: Petsense by Tractor Supply Kicks off 20th Birthday "Pawty" With Nearly $1 Million in Donations to Local Shelters
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., August 28, 2025--Petsense by Tractor Supply, a wholly owned subsidiary of Tractor Supply Co. (NASDAQ: TSCO), is throwing a "20th Birthday PAWTY" this September to celebrate two decades of serving pets out here. Rural America’s go-to pet specialty retailer is holding a month-long celebration to highlight nearly $1 million in donations to local animal shelters this year, a new national campaign with K9s For Warriors, in-store discounts, weekly giveaways and more.
